40:09.102 --> 40:10.364
Kathy.

40:10.408 --> 40:11.409
Kathy!

40:15.282 --> 40:16.370
Kathy.

40:26.989 --> 40:29.078
- We can wake...
- Wake up!

40:29.122 --> 40:31.080
