41:30.357 --> 41:31.637
Get away!

41:31.663 --> 41:33.795
Scaring the children.

42:10.658 --> 42:12.921
Wake up,
wake up, wake up.

42:22.627 --> 42:23.627
Hey.

42:24.542 --> 42:25.847
Rick, what's...

42:27.022 --> 42:28.154
