42:29.982 --> 42:31.200
Are you okay?

42:44.387 --> 42:45.911
Stay awake, Rick.

42:47.869 --> 42:50.002
Come on, I know you can.

42:57.749 --> 42:59.402
Wake up, young man!

43:00.534 --> 43:01.970
Wake up!

43:02.014 --> 43:04.364
Wake up, young man!

44:49.512 --> 44:50.731
And you...

44:50.775 --> 44:52.820
This one's
gonna be you, Browning.

44:52.864 --> 44:53.908
I'll find you.

44:57.956 --> 44:59.305
This is you.

44:59.348 --> 45:00.915
I know this...

45:00.959 --> 45:01.611
- This one's gotta be you.
- Hello?

45:01.655 --> 45:02.830
Hello, yes.

45:02.874 --> 45:04.614
Yes, I got your, um...

45:04.658 --> 45:06.573
I got your number
