45:11.447 --> 45:13.188
- What are you talking about?
- Huh?

45:13.232 --> 45:14.712
Is your daughter Clarissa?

45:14.755 --> 45:16.254
- What? Get lost.
- I know it's you, Browning.

45:16.278 --> 45:17.342
- Browning. Browning!
- Go to hell.

45:18.454 --> 45:20.805
Shit!

45:20.848 --> 45:22.937
Stay awake, Rick.
Stay... Stay awake.

45:28.290 --> 45:29.901
That clock's not right, is it?

45:29.944 --> 45:32.251
What do you mean?
It was... It's 135 hours.

45:32.294 --> 45:33.731
You trying to screw
with me, dude?

45:33.774 --> 45:34.838
No, why would I do that?

45:34.862 --> 45:36.211
