45:36.255 --> 45:37.125
- No, I promise you. Why...
- You're, like, getting

45:37.169 --> 45:38.257
really helpful, Miguel.

45:38.300 --> 45:39.625
- Why would I do that?
- Thanks, dude.

45:39.649 --> 45:40.868
What's going on, man?

45:40.912 --> 45:42.150
- I'm so fucking sorry.
