45:51.705 --> 45:53.074
- What the hell?
- I don't know, Rick.

45:53.098 --> 45:54.553
- What is going on?
- What is this about?

45:54.577 --> 45:56.338
- What happened to him?
- This is unbelievable!

45:56.362 --> 45:58.103
- Rick, just...
- Dude.

45:58.146 --> 45:59.582
