- You need to just calm down.

46:03.064 --> 46:04.544
Relax. Have you eaten?
Did he eat?

46:04.587 --> 46:06.546
- He drank. He, he...
- Has he eaten something?

46:06.589 --> 46:08.113
Is Kathy there?

46:08.156 --> 46:09.201
Who is he calling?

46:09.244 --> 46:10.637
If she, you know... Wait, wait.

46:10.680 --> 46:12.073
Is, um...

46:12.117 --> 46:14.162
