46:24.520 --> 46:25.840
- I can't do this.
- Yes, you can.

46:25.870 --> 46:27.175
You can do this.
You can do this.

46:27.219 --> 46:28.786
Yeah...

46:28.829 --> 46:30.111
- I gotta get out...
