50:55.182 --> 50:56.792
You're a good liar.

50:56.836 --> 50:58.664
No, you're the liar, Browning.

50:58.707 --> 51:01.406
No Clarissa died from SMA
in the past 30 years.

51:01.449 --> 51:03.625
